messages.text: Welcome! I'm Anita Bhargava, strategic financial advisor and co-founder of Bharosa Club. I'm excited to explore your financial journey together and help create a strategic plan that aligns with your unique lifestyle and aspirations. Today, we'll focus on understanding your current lifestyle choices and future goals - not just the numbers, but the story behind them. This foundation will help us develop a personalized strategy for building sustainable wealth that truly reflects who you are. Let's define success on your own terms. To begin, could you please tell me your name and age?
